net.ttddyy.dsproxy.transform

Class TransformInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.ttddyy.dsproxy.transform.TransformInfo

  • public class TransformInfo
extends Object
    Hold context information for ParameterTransformer.transformParameters(ParameterReplacer, TransformInfo).

    • clazz: calling class. PreparedStatement or CallableStatement
    • dataSourceName: datasource name
    • query: query string
    • isBatch: true when called in batch
    • count: current number of call in batch. 0 origin. 0 if call is not batched

    Semantics of isBatch():

    For QueryTransformer, isBatch() is only true when Statement.addBatch(String) is called. isBatch() is always false for PreparedStatement and CallableStatement. For ParameterTransformer, isBatch() returns true when PreparedStatement.addBatch() or PreparedStatement.addBatch() is called.

    Since:
    1.2
    Author:
    Tadaya Tsuyukubo
    See Also:
    ParameterTransformer, QueryTransformer
